<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV66">
<l>uṇṇā tuṟaṅkā tuṇarvuṟu mettaṉai yōkiyarkku</l>
<l>meṇṇāy miḷiru miyalviṉa vāmeri nīrvaḷivāṉ</l>
<l>maṇṇā kiyavem perumāṉ taṉatuvai kuntamaṉṉāḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṇā yaruviṉai yēṉuyi rāyiṉa kāvikaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For any Yogin who has consciousness without eating [and] slumbering</l>
<l>they are of a nature that flashes as thoughts – the lotuses that are the life</l>
<l>of me who has difficult Karma, being the eyes of her who is like Vaikuntam</l>
<l>of our great lord who is fire, water, wind, sky [and] earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
